dera finis dalam ajang balap MotoGP Mandalika sedang hangat dibicarakan publik.\\n\"Sebuah kehormatan bisa mengibarkan bendera finish di MotoGP,\" tulis akun @maiaestiantyreal, dilansir pada Senin 30 September 2024.\\nDalam akun Instagram pribadinya, Maia Estianty menceritakan pengalaman pertama kali mengibarkan bendera finis MotoGP. Dia mengaku gugup hingga overthingking dapat menunaikan tugasnya.\\n\"Aku senang banget karena bisa berpartisipasi dalam acara MotoGP yang ditonton sedunia. Sebelum naik itu deg-degan, kayak, 'Aku bisa nggak ya ngibarin bendera itu? Apakah berat? Apakah bakal meleset?'\" kata Maia Estianty.\\nBaca Juga: InJourney Libatkan 3.000 SDM Lokal Pada Pertamina Grand Prix of Indonesia 2024, Presiden Jokowi Berikan Apresiasi\\nKendati gugup, mantan istri Ahmad Dhani itu sukses menunaikan tugasnya sebagai pengibar bendera finis MotoGP di Sirkuit mandalika.\\nKetika pembalap MotoGP asal Spanyol Jorge Martin melintasi garis akhir, ibunda El Rumi tersebut mengibarkan bendera finis tanpa dibantu Marshal.\\nDari unggahan yang beredar, Maia Estianty tampil dalam balutan busana daster motif bunga. Dia tampak energik saat mengibarkan bendera finis.\\nLantaran mendapat privilege mengibarkan bendera finis di Sirkuit Mandalika, Maia Estianty ditodong warganet perihal syarat menjadi pengibar bendera finis.\\n\"Bun kalau ngibarin begini, ada syarat khusus nggak? Misalnya score TOEFL berapa? IPK berapa? Bisa menguasai excel atau apa gitu? Jadi pengin,\" tulis seorang netizen.\\nBaca Juga: Jerome Polin Kembali Dituding Bawa Sial, Kini 3 Pembalap di MotoGP Mandalika 2024 Jadi \"Korban\"\\nMaia Estianty mengungkap, alasan dirinya bisa didapuk sebagai pengibar bendera finis di Sikurit Mandalika adalah karena bantuan orang dalam.\\n\"Yang penting punya suami, sih. Dan jalur orang dalam,\" kata Maia Estianty.\\nUntuk informasi, Irwan Mussry adalah CEO Time International, sebuah perusahaan yang mengelola toko ritel untuk merek-merek terkemuka di bidang fesyen, jam tangan, dan perhiasan.\\nTisset merupakan salah satu brand yang ikut dikelola dan jadi sponsor utama MotoGP.\\nMaka tak heran, Irwan Mussry juga mendapat kesempatkan mengalungi medali untuk pembalap MotoGP Mandalika.</td>\n","    </tr>\n","  </tbody>\n","</table>\n","</div>\n","    <div class=\"colab-df-buttons\">\n","\n","  <div class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","    <button class=\"colab-df-convert\" onclick=\"convertToInteractive('df-26e2fdd6-8284-4274-8b75-574f369f4495')\"\n","            title=\"Convert this dataframe to an interactive table.\"\n","            style=\"display:none;\">\n","\n","  <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\">\n","    <path d=\"M120-120v-720h720v720H120Zm60-500h600v-160H180v160Zm220 220h160v-160H400v160Zm0 220h160v-160H400v160ZM180-400h160v-160H180v160Zm440 0h160v-160H620v160ZM180-180h160v-160H180v160Zm440 0h160v-160H620v160Z\"/>\n","  </svg>\n","    </button>\n","\n","  <style>\n","    .colab-df-container {\n","      display:flex;\n","      gap: 12px;\n","    }\n","\n","    .colab-df-convert {\n","      background-color: #E8F0FE;\n","      border: none;\n","      border-radius: 50%;\n","      cursor: pointer;\n","      display: none;\n","      fill: #1967D2;\n","      height: 32px;\n","      padding: 0 0 0 0;\n","      width: 32px;\n","    }\n","\n","    .colab-df-convert:hover {\n","      background-color: #E2EBFA;\n","      box-shadow: 0px 1px 2px rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.3), 0px 1px 3px 1px rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.15);\n","      fill: #174EA6;\n","    }\n","\n","    .colab-df-buttons div {\n","      margin-bottom: 4px;\n","    }\n","\n","    [theme=dark] .colab-df-convert {\n","      background-color: #3B4455;\n","      fill: #D2E3FC;\n","    }\n","\n","    [theme=dark] .colab-df-convert:hover {\n","      background-color: #434B5C;\n","      box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n","      filter: drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3));\n","      fill: #FFFFFF;\n","    }\n","  </style>\n